Explanatory Note

On October 11, 2024, The Toronto-Dominion Bank
(the Bank) filed, on Form 6-K (the Previous
6-K), plea agreements in connection with the
United States v. TD Bank, N.A. and United
States v. TD Bank US Holding Company (the
Plea Agreements). The Bank is refiling the
Plea Agreements
as Exhibit 99.1 and 99.2 hereto to include
appendices that were originally redacted in
the exhibits filed with the Previous 6-K.
